WEBVTT

00:05:28.443 --> 00:05:31.809
he would correctly declare,
"Beethoven!"

00:05:31.809 --> 00:05:34.665
But Kanner took a dim view
of these abilities,

00:05:34.665 --> 00:05:38.242
claiming that the kids
were just regurgitating things

00:05:38.242 --> 00:05:40.865
they'd heard their pompous parents say,

00:05:40.865 --> 00:05:43.465
desperate to earn their approval.

00:05:43.465 --> 00:05:48.829
As a result, autism became
a source of shame and stigma for families,

00:05:48.829 --> 00:05:51.406
and two generations of autistic children

00:05:51.406 --> 00:05:54.889
were shipped off to institutions
for their own good,

00:05:54.889 --> 00:05:58.163
becoming invisible to the world at large.

00:05:58.163 --> 00:06:02.400
Amazingly, it wasn't until the 1970s